race.comment: SPEEDY DEVILLE (1) was always prominent from this same draw last time and boxed on well to place (22.00) in a Grade 5 over 381m at this track. Expected to feature again. BOLT OF FUN (7) won again in another strong performance after leading recording back to back wins, scoring by 1.3 lengths (21.91) at this track over 381m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Form should stack up. LIBERTY STAR (2) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the minors latest when third (16.26) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Expecting another good run. KILLER KELLY (4) is worth consideration after filling a hole at this course and distance last start.
